      • getGmax

        public float getGmax(double mass)
        get max load factor of current mass the max load factor is determind by mass of aircraft if mass is less than design weight, maxG is design G limit, if is more than design weight, Gmax = Gdesign*designWeight/curretnWeight
        参数:
        mass - current weight
        返回:
        the g limit of current weight
